            {
              "cf": "",
              "x": "The medieval cathedral was adorned with grotesque gargoyles, which served both as decorative elements and functional rain spouts."
            },
            {
              "cf": "",
              "x": "The Gothic castle's ramparts were lined with menacing gargoyles, their twisted forms striking fear into the hearts of attackers."
            },
            {
              "cf": "",
              "x": "The Renaissance palace had ornate balustrades topped with sculpted gargoyles, adding a touch of whimsy to the architectural design."
            },
            {
              "cf": "",
              "x": "The Art Deco skyscraper featured sleek, stylized gargoyles that reflected the modernist aesthetic of the era."
            },
            {
              "cf": "",
